cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.SI 

This paper deals with machine learning models and algorithmic decision making, which are core topics in the field of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also addresses issues related to fairness and discrimination, which are relevant to the subfield of cybersecurity (cs.CR) and social and information networks (cs.SI). Finally, the proposed active framework for fair classification involves adaptive information acquisition, which could be related to the subfield of cybernetics (cs.CY).
